sentences: Matt Maeson (born January 17, 1993) is an American singer-songwriter and musician from Virginia Beach, Virginia, signed to Neon Gold Records and Atlantic Records.
He did community service by working construction for 12 hours a day and performed at biker rallies and prisons with his parents' ministry.
